{"about_the_game":"Some suspected that Mars once harbored life. <br />\r\nThere was a reason that it wasn't ever found.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMines of Mars is a procedural atmospheric mining game that is inspired by games like Metroid and Motherload. <br />\r\nIt is also a story based adventure game with dark secrets, great weapons, tons of different items, and a gorgeous world to explore. <br />\r\nThe world of MoM is procedurally created, so that every time you play it, it will be a little different. <br />\r\nThere are tons of different enemies, dark corridors, and a large variety of fauna and ambient creatures. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Huge Procedurally generated underground world <br />\r\n-Night and Day system <br />\r\n-Dark secrets <br />\r\n-Atmospheric vibes <br />\r\n-3 Mini Games<br />\r\n-Original Ambient Soundtrack by Evan Gipson <br />\r\n-Lots of flora and fauna <br />\r\n-Tons of Weapons and Items <br />\r\n-Great storyline <br />\r\n-Gravity Mining! <br />\r\n-Huge Bosses <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFollow us for the latest info and game news!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u2022 http://crescentmoongames.com/other-games/<br />\r\n\u2022 http://facebook.com/crescentmoongames<br />\r\n\u2022 http://twitter.com/cm_games","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Monster Killed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/413740/eac021094902003e7a98addfcb6ec836d43283f7.jpg"},{"name":"First Mineral Mined","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/413740/f9a4887ad62f6a63276b83b1ad3df88eecf37278.jpg"},{"name":"First Gem Mined","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/413740/c897d227d471541775f014b2485583961475b908.jpg"},{"name":"First Statue Found","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/413740/e8acb4665b5938e3ab5c362718ec69113df7ed48.jpg"},{"name":"Secound Statue Found","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/ima